The little part is a part of the card you can cast as an Adventure, they're always instants or sorceries and after their effect happens, they get exiled. Then later you can cast the other half of the card. Kinda like two cards in one, but you can cast the creature half to start with and ignore the adventure.
The Role thing was given to a lot of cards and a lot of different type of role tokens can be made (like monster gives +1/+1 and trample, or cursed makes it a 1/1). If you make a role token and put it on something that already has a role, all the other ones fall off, so a creature can only be one role at a time.
